<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: farming outpost -->
  <Outpost_Farming.label>农场据点</Outpost_Farming.label>
  <!-- EN: Places a temporary, autonomously-led camp that specializes in sowing and harvesting easily-grown vegetation, cannot be placed on deserts. Once an ample amount is collected, a delivery will be made at the outskirts of a faction's primary colony. -->
  <Outpost_Farming.description>一处能够自给自足的临时性据点，专门负责种植并收获容易生长的农作物。一旦收集至足够的数量，驻守在此据点的殖民者将会把粮食作物交付至派系主殖民地的指定地点。无法建立在沙漠地形上。</Outpost_Farming.description>
  <!-- EN: Choose which plant this outpost should plant -->
  <Outpost_Farming.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>选择此据点要种植的作物。</Outpost_Farming.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>
  <!-- EN: Choose plant -->
  <Outpost_Farming.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>选择作物</Outpost_Farming.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: hunting outpost -->
  <Outpost_Hunting.label>狩猎据点</Outpost_Hunting.label>
  <!-- EN: Places a temporary, autonomously-led camp that specializes in hunting and butchering wildlife. Once an ample amount is collected, a delivery will be made at the outskirts of a faction's primary colony. -->
  <Outpost_Hunting.description>一处能够自给自足的临时性据点，专门负责狩猎并屠宰野生动物。一旦收集至足够的数量，驻守在此据点的殖民者将会把鲜肉皮革交付至派系主殖民地的指定地点。</Outpost_Hunting.description>
  <!-- EN: Choose what animal to hunt at this outpost -->
  <Outpost_Hunting.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>选择此据点要狩猎的动物。</Outpost_Hunting.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>
  <!-- EN: Hunting {0} -->
  <Outpost_Hunting.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>狩猎{0}</Outpost_Hunting.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>
  
  <!-- EN: logging outpost -->
  <Outpost_Logging.label>伐木据点</Outpost_Logging.label>
  <!-- EN: Places a temporary, autonomously-led camp that specializes in collecting wood from trees in the areas, cannot be placed on deserts. Once an ample amount is collected, a delivery will be made at the outskirts of a faction's primary colony. -->
  <Outpost_Logging.description>一处能够自给自足的临时性据点，专门负责采伐此地区的树木。一旦收集至足够的数量，驻守在此据点的殖民者将会把木材交付至派系主殖民地的指定地点。</Outpost_Logging.description>
  
  <!-- EN: mining outpost -->
  <Outpost_Mining.label>采矿据点</Outpost_Mining.label>
  <!-- EN: Places a temporary, autonomously-led camp that specializes in collecting and processing stone or metal, can only be placed on hills or mountains. Once an ample amount is collected, a delivery will be made at the outskirts of a faction's primary colony. -->
  <Outpost_Mining.description>一处能够自给自足的临时性据点，专门负责开采加工石块或金属。一旦收集至足够的数量，驻守在此据点的殖民者将会把矿物石砖交付至派系主殖民地的指定地点。必须建立在丘陵或山地地形上。</Outpost_Mining.description>
  <!-- EN: Click to change mining target. -->
  <Outpost_Mining.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>点击来改变开采目标</Outpost_Mining.modExtensions.0.ChooseDesc>
  <!-- EN: Mining {0} -->
  <Outpost_Mining.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>开采{0}</Outpost_Mining.modExtensions.0.ChooseLabel>
  
